docs.text:
Apex Launcher


About


The Apex Launcher is a modified version of Technic from 
HackPhoenix.com

built for ApexNet servers and uses the ApexNet authentication servers. Make sure to sign in with your
ApexNet username. On most servers, you must enter a PIN every login. You get this username and PIN when
you join ApexNet.


Download




Just put it on your desktop. That's it!


Servers


ApexNet Hexxit 24/7: 
apexnet.ga


ApexNet Affinity 24/7: 
apexnet.ga:1227


Modpacks


All Technic Modpacks are supported!


Apex Affinity


Coming March 2016. Battle your way through the tough world of Affinity, with classic
mods from Big Swords to Battletowers. As you fight your way into the world of fortune,
you will unconver the riches, never found in any other modpack on Apex. To vote for mods
or contribute, email me or join ApexNet community. This modpack is planned to be on
MC 7.1.2, 1.8, or 1.8.9. Any suggestions would be greatly appreciated.




The Elements V2: Unleashed


Coming April 2016. Fight your way to victory in this multiplayer bound pack where money 
is everything, so get out there and MAKE IT RAIN! Pile up the riches as you rise to the top, ruling
your empire and fighting to glory. Recruit and build your empire amoung yourself and
your friends in this never before seen, unleashed and ready to rumble modpack.




To submit a modpack that's not listed here, email us.


Contact


nexus331@gmail.com
